{
  "id": "class_0017",
  "name": "Cartographer of Sacred Winds",
  "title_completion": "a Cartographer of Sacred Winds",
  "flavor_text": "Armed with charcoal and consecrated parchment, she ascends the Tower each dawn to chart what the wind refuses to name. Her maps do not merely describe the world \u2014 they hold it still, fixing borders that the gale would otherwise erase. To be caught within her True Survey is to find yourself pinned to the page, a landmark in someone else's holy scripture.",
